title: Stiff Little Fingers - Hanx! [320Kbps CBR MP3 Vinyl Rip]
description:
Stiff Little Fingers - Hanx!
============================

Sampled from the original vinyl at 44KHz 16-bit Stereo
Scratch removal by Brian Davies&#039; ClickRepair v2.2.1
High frequency noise removal by Brian Davies&#039; DeNoise v1.0.1
Equalisation and normalisation by Audacity v1.3.4
ID3 Tags by TagScanner v5.0
MP3 Encoding at 320Kb/s CBR with LAME v3.97

Please note that I have played this record to death and over the
years the sound quality has deteriorated considerably. The record
has also accumulated many scratches which I have tried to eradicate.
